					"details": "Wire the animated horse nodes into the existing wagon presentation flow so normal gameplay, restart flow, return-to-title flow, and current wagon visual effects still work with the animated horse art. Keep both horses visually consistent with each other and write very thorough unit or scene tests for the affected behavior.\n\nDone when: by playing, restarting, and returning to the title, both horse animations keep working through the normal game flow and the wagon team still shows the expected hit, failure, and run-state presentation without obvious visual breakage.",
					"done": true
